tcp: add related fields into SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS

Add the following stats into SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS control msg:
    TCP_NLA_PACING_RATE
    TCP_NLA_DELIVERY_RATE
    TCP_NLA_SND_CWND
    TCP_NLA_REORDERING
    TCP_NLA_MIN_RTT
    TCP_NLA_RECUR_RETRANS
    TCP_NLA_DELIVERY_RATE_APP_LMT

